ml.optimization

Interface Projection

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProjL1, ProjL2, ProjLInfinity

    public interface Projection
    Compute proj_tC(X), which is defined by proj_tC(x) := argmin_{u \in tC} 1/2 * || u - x ||^2.
    Version:
    1.0 Jan. 25th, 2014
    Author:
    Mingjie Qian
